         <div type="comments">
            <p><note type="parallels"><ref type="ms" target="txt:m-a216"/> (completing); <ref type="ms" target="txt:m-yqii3"/>; <ref type="ms" target="txt:m-yqii4"/>; MaitrHami 2, 4-5</note><note type="philcomment">This fragment, complemented by <ref type="ms" target="txt:m-a216"/>, contains part of the second act of the Maitreyasamitināṭaka; it corresponds to <ref type="ms" target="txt:m-yqii3"/> b8 - <ref type="ms" target="txt:m-yqii4"/> b6. An Uy. parallel is MaitrHami II, 4a19-5a15. See also <bibl><title corresp="ref:pinault1999"/><citedRange>195-6</citedRange></bibl>.</note></p>
